

    The Antmod, modular Ant-based build system, project has announced the release of version 1.2.1. They write in, "Antmod 1.2.1 features new plugins for findbugs, tomcat, javadoc, jar, and javac. It contains various bugfixes and improvements in other build plugins. Some property names and directories have been made more consistent. This release is recommended for all current Antmod users."
   

